# 🌍 GeoTrade AI System – Phase 1 Documentation

## 📌 Overview

This project builds an AI-powered geopolitical trading assistant that:

* Fetches real-time geopolitical news
* Uses a local LLM (Ollama + Llama 3)
* Generates trading insights (Buy/Sell/Hold)

